 platforms, allowing the group to blend in with normal activity and operate with reduced risk of detection."], ["confidence", null], ["execution_start", null], ["execution_end", null]], "anchors": {"0": "76f02506-26ba-4646-be88-bafa2723e865", "30": "79a40dbb-d8e3-4c9e-9067-1cd63e582a1d", "60": "e92125ef-2687-4192-a697-1a981be4cb21", "90": "b784cc9a-27d9-45cf-a5d2-dc2d3da6cd1d", "120": "e5a06ceb-215c-4a9a-bcad-a61348f2c5c1", "150": "53c82ad9-ef91-40b1-8cba-09ed37d88cab", "180": "7a5cb228-1a21-421f-839f-9e60ccc665f6", "210": "70526523-869d-44d6-9b10-2d1efe79ce05", "240": "dfa7779f-29c2-46be-9977-f4d0de228e13", "270": "f98c8af2-951e-44cf-8556-6f668bcfa807", "300": "81707594-e687-4354-86af-805b3ba313a7", "330": "f3b97679-aeb9-4a68-9370-2b56752b19b5"}}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "f6426b21-92db-4d84-a27c-2ac2a5dac01f", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "eea2b4c0-2303-4430-8694-8491d2fb9479", "latches": []}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "1b6e688a-0f61-40d6-8bec-adcf91c1d0f7", "latches": []}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "9e054f02-a03f-4823-8ba8-b8aecbdb2d13", "latches": ["5b17d775-54ed-4508-930a-8b791e969876"]}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "1cea6068-5f33-4f65-8263-01c060faa05f", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "f7673680-c944-40d8-a882-8abbc30421a7", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "f6b91e14-1e15-4a91-9d60-994bd8399a5f", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "a0156046-49f6-40ca-868d-128016f106ec", "latches": []}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "163677c9-ad62-4282-aacb-03a2bd45201d", "latches": []}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "630b27e9-9712-45c9-bbef-922f67452ccc", "latches": []}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "e9fb949f-8656-44d5-80b2-05b8e7224115", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "c952ff9f-b173-464f-9f8d-f0e21fb3f1d4", "latches": []}, {"id": "action", "instance": "5e43f941-9550-4a8e-a4c5-5ec8025cb9ef", "properties": [["name", "Exploit Public-Facing Application"], ["ttp", [["tactic", "TA0001"], ["technique", "T1190"]]], ["description", "INC ransomware affiliates exploit vulnerabilities in internet-facing applications and services to gain initial access. Successful exploitation provides a foothold on externally exposed systems and a path to pivot into internal networks ahead of credential theft, lateral movement, and ransomware deployment."], ["confidence", null], ["execution_start", null], ["execution_end", null]], "anchors": {"0": "f6426b21-92db-4d84-a27c-2ac2a5dac01f", "30": "eea2b4c0-2303-4430-8694-8491d2fb9479", "60": "1b6e688a-0f61-40d6-8bec-adcf91c1d0f7", "90": "9e054f02-a03f-4823-8ba8-b8aecbdb2d13", "120": "1cea6068-5f33-4f65-8263-01c060faa05f", "150": "f7673680-c944-40d8-a882-8abbc30421a7", "180": "f6b91e14-1e15-4a91-9d60-994bd8399a5f", "210": "a0156046-49f6-40ca-868d-128016f106ec", "240": "163677c9-ad62-4282-aacb-03a2bd45201d", "270": "630b27e9-9712-45c9-bbef-922f67452ccc", "300": "e9fb949f-8656-44d5-80b2-05b8e7224115", "330": "c952ff9f-b173-464f-9f8d-f0e21fb3f1d4"}}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "862d1bf6-ffc4-4763-8e46-29b73b039ec6", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "3bff6075-6fe3-4c2e-9cfb-17753817e104", "latches": ["e770f97d-7057-4a7c-951e-3063ec0a9383"]}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "44d911be-cbd4-4aff-85ea-58fe05aa8bfd", "latches": ["12aaec9f-18f1-4cea-bac8-600e47147d89"]}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "f1271ca6-6dfc-4d50-b274-00bf6d2e0183", "latches": ["94769d30-27b7-4c6b-b538-50d4acc8f2ca"]}, {"id": "vertical_anchor", "instance": "bbee5aed-b881-478d-b146-111c2185da66", "latches": ["ae2aa9da-4b71-4771-baf4-4d0461465532"]}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "b627ffff-d8a3-4ae4-ac32-68cc05804128", "latches": ["a9e5c314-e10a-45e3-9fdc-5a1296354e2b"]}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "132aa76b-a9ba-4120-915e-fe44758b1c42", "latches": []}, {"id": "horizontal_anchor", "instance": "05